    "causal_summary": "Investigate whether BAAI/bge-reranker-v2-m3 is the right cross-encoder for code-retrieval queries on a 4-mirror codebase. The May 18 evening instrumented bench surfaced a structural failure mode: the reranker demotes implementations below tests/refs on paraphrase-heavy queries (lexical-cue density rewarded over semantic role). This packet researches alternative cross-encoder reranker models trained on code (or code-adjacent retrieval), measures the four failure-case probes (3, 10, 14, 18) against the alternatives, and recommends a swap if any alternative materially improves the failure-mode pattern.",
